<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="154" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1125,1296]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154">
Comments: 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure, J. S." box="[289,448,1125,1151]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" pagination="257 - 261" refId="ref19344" refString="Moure, J. S. (2002) O subgenero Centris (Aphemisia) Ayala: notas complementares e descricao de uma nova especie (Hymenoptera, Apoidea). Revista Brasileira de Entomologia, 46 (3), 257 - 261. https: // doi. org / 10.1590 / S 0085 - 56262002000300006" type="journal article" year="2002">Moure (2002)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned the existence of a 
<typeStatus box="[795,843,1125,1151]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154">type</typeStatus>
series of this species, but 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure, J. S. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F." box="[1149,1374,1125,1151]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" pagination="83 - 142" refId="ref19543" refString="Moure, J. S., Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F. (2007) Centridini Cockerell &amp; Cockerell. In: Moure, J. S., Urban, D. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. (Orgs.), Catalogue of Bees (Hymenoptera, Apoidea) in the Neotropical Region. Sociedade Brasileira de Entomologia, Curitiba, pp. 83 - 142." type="book chapter" year="2007">
Moure 
<emphasis box="[1232,1284,1125,1151]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="154">et al</emphasis>
. (2007)
</bibRefCitation>
indicated erroneously that it was described based on a single female specimen collected in Santarém. According to the NHMUK accession book and the information of the lectotype’s label, the specimens were collected in Tapajos River, not in Santarém as indicated by 
<bibRefCitation author="Smith, F." box="[594,746,1232,1259]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" pagination="199 - 465" refId="ref19938" refString="Smith, F. (1854) Catalogue of Hymenopterous Insects in the Collection of the British Museum. Part 2. British Museum, London, 267 pp. [pp. 199 - 465]" type="book chapter" year="1854">Smith (1854)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[759,950,1233,1259]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="plumipes">
<emphasis box="[759,950,1233,1259]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="154">Centris plumipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was correctly interpreted by 
<bibRefCitation author="Ayala, R." box="[1282,1432,1233,1259]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" pagination="1 - 8" refId="ref17542" refString="Ayala, R. (2002) Two new subgenera of bees in the genus Centris (Hymenoptera: Apidae). Scientific Papers, Natural History Museum The University of Kansas, 25, 1 - 8. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8484" type="journal article" year="2002">Ayala (2002)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Silveira, F. A. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Almeida, E. A. B." box="[151,385,1269,1295]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" refId="ref19793" refString="Silveira, F. A., Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Almeida, E. A. B. (2002) Abelhas brasileiras Sistematica e Identificacao. Fundacao Araucaria, Belo Horizonte, 254 pp." type="book" year="2002">
Silveira 
<emphasis box="[245,294,1269,1295]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="154">et al</emphasis>
. (2002)
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Moure, J. S. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F." box="[397,616,1269,1295]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" pagination="83 - 142" refId="ref19543" refString="Moure, J. S., Melo, G. A. R. &amp; Vivallo, F. (2007) Centridini Cockerell &amp; Cockerell. In: Moure, J. S., Urban, D. &amp; Melo, G. A. R. (Orgs.), Catalogue of Bees (Hymenoptera, Apoidea) in the Neotropical Region. Sociedade Brasileira de Entomologia, Curitiba, pp. 83 - 142." type="book chapter" year="2007">
Moure 
<emphasis box="[479,528,1269,1295]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="154">et al</emphasis>
. (2007)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Vivallo, F. &amp; Velez, D. &amp; Fernandez, F." box="[670,900,1269,1296]" pageId="3" pageNumber="154" pagination="201 - 216" refId="ref21251" refString="Vivallo, F., Velez, D. &amp; Fernandez, F. (2016) Two new species of Centris (Aphemisia) Ayala, 2002 from Colombia with a synopsis of the subgenus for the country (Hymenoptera: Apidae: Centridini). Zootaxa, 4093 (2), 201 - 216. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4093.2.3" type="journal article" year="2016">
Vivallo 
<emphasis box="[759,809,1269,1295]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="154">et al</emphasis>
. (2016)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
